---

<section id="proyecto" class="section intro">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="intro-content fade-in">
      <span class="section-tag">El Proyecto</span>
      <h2>Patrimonio y modernidad<br>en perfecta armonía</h2>
      <p>En el corazón de Santoña, junto al Ayuntamiento y la histórica Plaza de San Antonio, recuperamos un edificio centenario para crear ocho viviendas únicas y dos locales comerciales. Un proyecto que combina la riqueza patrimonial con las más altas calidades constructivas contemporáneas.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="caracteristicas" class="section features">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="features-wrapper">
      <div class="features-header fade-in">
        <h3>Características destacadas</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature fade-in" data-delay="0.1">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              <polyline points="9,22 9,12 15,12 15,22" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-content">
            <h4>Ubicación Excepcional</h4>
            <p>En pleno centro histórico, a pasos del Ayuntamiento, Plaza de San Antonio y Palacio de Manzanedo. Un enclave único en la villa marinera más auténtica de Cantabria.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="feature fade-in" data-delay="0.2">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path d="M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 0 1-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 0 1-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 0 1 7.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-content">
            <h4>Rehabilitación Cuidada</h4>
            <p>Recuperación integral respetando materiales originales: tejas históricas, rejerías y elementos constructivos tradicionales combinados con tecnología actual.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="feature fade-in" data-delay="0.3">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/>
              <line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              <line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="21" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-content">
            <h4>Viviendas Singulares</h4>
            <p>Ocho viviendas de 2 y 3 dormitorios con techos de gran altura, cocinas integradas y amplios miradores que recuperan la fachada señorial original.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="feature fade-in" data-delay="0.4">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              <path d="M2 17l10 5 10-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              <path d="M2 12l10 5 10-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-content">
            <h4>Espacios Comunitarios</h4>
            <p>Patio interior rehabilitado que ofrece un oasis de tranquilidad en el centro urbano, perfecto para el encuentro y las actividades comunitarias.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .intro {
    background: var(--white);
    padding: 120px 0 80px 0;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 20px;
  }

  .intro-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .section-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    color: var(--primary);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .section-tag::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -8px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 40px;
    height: 2px;
    background: var(--primary);
  }

  .intro h2 {
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--dark);
    margin-bottom: 30px;
    line-height: 1.2;
    letter-spacing: -1px;
  }

  .intro p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--gray-600);
    font-weight: 300;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .features {
    background: var(--light);
    padding: 100px 0;
  }

  .features-wrapper {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .features-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 80px;
  }

  .features-header h3 {
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--dark);
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 60px 80px;
    margin-top: 60px;
  }

  .feature {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 25px;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(30px);
    transition: all 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
  }

  .feature.in-view {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }

  .feature-icon {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 50px;
    height: 50px;
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--primary);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 103, 144, 0.1);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .feature:hover .feature-icon {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 103, 144, 0.15);
  }

  .feature-content h4 {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--dark);
    margin-bottom: 15px;
    letter-spacing: -0.3px;
  }

  .feature-content p {
    color: var(--gray-600);
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  /* Animations */
  .fade-in {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(30px);
    transition: all 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
  }

  .fade-in.in-view {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }

  .fade-in[data-delay="0.1"] { transition-delay: 0.1s; }
  .fade-in[data-delay="0.2"] { transition-delay: 0.2s; }
  .fade-in[data-delay="0.3"] { transition-delay: 0.3s; }
  .fade-in[data-delay="0.4"] { transition-delay: 0.4s; }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .intro {
      padding: 100px 0 60px 0;
    }
    
    .features {
      padding: 80px 0;
    }
    
    .features-grid {
      gap: 50px 60px;
    }
    
    .features-header {
      margin-bottom: 60px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .intro h2 {
      font-size: 2.8rem;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
    }
    
    .intro p {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
    
    .features-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 40px;
      margin-top: 40px;
    }
    
    .feature {
      gap: 20px;
    }
    
    .feature-icon {
      width: 45px;
      height: 45px;
    }
    
    .features-header h3 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .intro h2 {
      font-size: 2.4rem;
    }
    
    .feature {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
      gap: 15px;
    }
    
    .feature-icon {
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
  }
</style>

<script>
  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
    // Initialize Intersection Observer for staggered animations
    const observerOptions = {
      threshold: 0.1,
      rootMargin: '0px 0px -50px 0px'
    };

    const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
      entries.forEach(entry => {
        if (entry.isIntersecting) {
          entry.target.classList.add('in-view');
        }
      });
    }, observerOptions);

    // Observe all animated elements
    const animatedElements = document.querySelectorAll('.fade-in, .feature');
    animatedElements.forEach(element => {
      observer.observe(element);
    });
  });
</script>